{
  "stem": "22869.5",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And everybody who stayed there was liberated in Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not one person died.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not the infirmary, not the ones who were hiding.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was-- I mean, after the war, it was-- we felt like fools, you know, that like we had freedom in our hands.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Russians liberated these guys.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Anyway, we were in Gleiwitz.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And in Gleiwitz they let us sleep over.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I remember we slept-- I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I think 36 hours or something.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I remember everybody was beat, I mean.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "After that, they gave us again-- and they resumed giving us all kinds of foods.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they loaded us in trains, cattle trains.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we began a new epoch, so to say, a new way of life, all different from what we were used to in the last few months.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we're heading now-- running away from the Russians, we're heading into deep Germany with the trains.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Now, again, you're piled up there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I don't recall now, but I remember I took from Auschwitz a pair of shoes that were real high shoes.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You know, they lace up almost to the middle of your foot.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I had good socks and everything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The only mistake I made, that in the night I did not take the shoes off, so my feet froze.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Because you're talking about January in Gleiwitz.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "That is January, February in Detroit with 10 below.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "That's the kind of temperature you're talking about-- unheated cattle train.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I mean, the only pleasure we had is hugging, maybe, each other to get a little warmth.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But it was awful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It was awful.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They dragged us, I don't recall exactly, but two or three days they dragged us into deep Germany.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we came to a city that is called Zolstadt.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
